  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "High-Speed RJ45 Module",
      "text": "The MikroTik S+RJ10 module is designed to provide high-speed connections over RJ45 copper cables via the SFP+ interface. It provides data transfer speeds of up to 10 Gbps, allowing you to upgrade your existing infrastructure without the need for fiber optic cabling. With support for 10GBASE-T, 5GBASE-T, 2.5GBASE-T, and 1000BASE-T standards, the module is compatible with various operating scenarios and provides flexibility in building modern networks. The most efficient performance is achieved in MikroTik devices with active cooling, but the module can also be used in equipment with passive cooling, provided that additional heat dissipation is ensured."
    },
    {
      "heading": "High-Speed RJ45 Module",
      "text": "Features:"
    },
    {
      "heading": "High-Speed RJ45 Module",
      "text": "Based on Marvell 88X3310P\nPower consumption 2.4 W max (10GBASE-T, 30 m link)\nCan only be used in SFP+ ports"
    },
